org.qbroker.monitor

Class GenericList

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.qbroker.monitor.Report
      • org.qbroker.monitor.GenericList
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MonitorReport

    public class GenericList
extends Report
    GenericList queries a data source for a list of keys. The list of the keys will be stored in a List under the key of "List" in the report.

    This needs more work to support other data sources.
    Author:
    yannanlu@yahoo.com
